# Default frontend repository path

When the user asks to change or review frontend code but does not specify a path with `@...`, assume the frontend repository is located at:

- `/Users/sx/Documents/workSpace/didi-taxi-front`

Use that directory as the default root for searching, reading, and editing frontend files (e.g. pages, API clients, routes) related to this backend repo.

# Frontend subprojects in this repo

Within `/Users/sx/Documents/workSpace/didi-taxi-front`, treat these directories as:

- `didi-driver-h5`: driver-side app (司机端)
- `didi-passenger-h5`: passenger-side app (乘客端)
- `didi-Vue`: admin console (后台管理平台)

